Text: Your Ofoto membershiplarry Thanks for joining Ofoto Your account has been credited with FREE x prints Whether youre into film or digital photography Ofoto delivers the best prints youve ever seen right to your door Here are a few of the most popular ways to use Ofoto Get FREE film processing and highresolution scanning on your first two rolls Store all of your digital photos on a secure Web site at no charge Invite family and friends to view your online photo albums Order beautiful prints on premium Kodak paper hours a day days a week The next time you visit Ofoto at youll need to log in using the email address and password you provided at registration Email address If you forget your password go to and click on the Forgot your password link under the Sign In box Now you can earn free prints for each friend you refer to Ofoto Refer friends and get up to free prints Go to Tellafriendjsp to refer your friends If you have any questions about using Ofoto just email us at Well be happy to help We hope you enjoy your prints from Ofoto Cheers James Joaquin President and CEO Ofoto Inc Ofoto Support Team Customer Support Email Customer Service Outside the US and Canada Customer Support Fax
